fm: int maxSubArray(vector<int> &nums) {         int size = nums.size(), prev = 0, curr = 0, ret = INT_MIN;         if (size == 0)             return 0;         for (int i = 0; i < nums.size(); ++i) {             int val = prev + nums[i];             ret = max(ret, val);             if (val > 0)                 curr = val;             else {                 if (nums[i] > 0)                     curr = nums[i];                 else                     curr = 0;             }             prev = curr;         }         return ret;     }

fm: int findPairs(vector<int> &nums, int k) {         map<int, int> knums;         int ret = 0;         for (auto num: nums)             ++knums[num];         for (auto m:knums) {             if (k == 0 && m.second > 1)                 ++ret;             else if (k > 0 && knums.find(m.first - k) != knums.end())                 ++ret;         }         return ret;     }

fm: string complexNumberMultiply(string a, string b) {         int plus1 = a.find('+'), end1 = a.find('i');         int x1 = stoi(a.substr(0, plus1)), y1 = stoi(a.substr(plus1 + 1, end1 - plus1 - 1));         int plus2 = b.find('+'), end2 = b.find('i');         int x2 = stoi(b.substr(0, plus2)), y2 = stoi(b.substr(plus2 + 1, end2 - plus2 - 1));         int x3 = x1 * x2 + y1 * y2 * -1, y3 = x1 * y2 + x2 * y1;         return to_string(x3) + '+' + to_string(y3) + 'i';     }
